Subject: drm/i915: Remove pointless dpll_funcs checks
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e87ba18b4c80cb4bb28a9a1b76edad79b34cb1fc
